== Specifications ==
The iPhone 16 and 16 Plus will have a vertical camera layout, similarly to the [[iPhone 12]]. Apple used a diagonal layout for [[iPhone 13]], [[iPhone 14]], and [[iPhone 15]], and Apple has not provided a reason as to why these models will switch back.

